from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(nums: List[int], target: int) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    n = len(nums)   # --- py stmt 3
    left, right = 0, n - 1   # --- py stmt 4
    while left < right:   # --- py stmt 5
        mid = (left + right) >> 1   # --- py stmt 6
        if nums[0] <= nums[mid]:   # --- py stmt 7
            if nums[0] <= target <= nums[mid]:   # --- py stmt 8
                right = mid   # --- py stmt 9
            else:
                left = mid + 1   # --- py stmt 10
        else:
            if nums[mid] < target <= nums[n - 1]:   # --- py stmt 11
                left = mid + 1   # --- py stmt 12
            else:
                right = mid   # --- py stmt 13
    return left if nums[left] == target else -1   # --- py stmt 14
```

    var right_index = n - 1;   // --- py stmt 4
    while (left_index < right_index) {   // --- py stmt 5
        var mid_index = (left_index + right_index) >> 1;   // --- py stmt 6
        if (nums[0] <= nums[mid_index]) {   // --- py stmt 7
            if (nums[0] <= target && target <= nums[mid_index]) {   // --- py stmt 8
                right_index = mid_index;   // --- py stmt 9
            }

                left_index = mid_index + 1;   // --- py stmt 10

                left_index = mid_index + 1;   // --- py stmt 12
